<p class="titular-large">
Major Functions of <i>Intelligent Reminder</i>
</p>
<ul class="body-emphasis">
    <li>Input items that you need to acquire or accomplish that are of a location-sensitive nature.</li>
    <li>Associate them with one or more locations.</li>
    <li><i>Intelligent Reminder</i> alerts you to those items at the time when you are in the vicinity of any one of the locations.</li>
</ul>
<p class="titular-large">
Important Characteristics of <i>Intelligent Reminder</i>
</p>
<ul class="body-emphasis">
    <li>You're list is always at hand.</li>
    <li><i>Intelligent Reminder</i> remembers your lists and locations, for future ease.</li>
</ul>
<p class="titular-large">
Advanced and Distictive Features of <i>Intelligent Reminder</i>
</p>
<ul>
<li>Network your lists with one or or other members ... securely, of course.  This means that when you input that you need, say,
dog food, then your associate will be alerted when he or she is at a place where this need can be fulfilled.
</li>
<li>Ability to group locations into a single "company".  (e.g. - Wal-Mart) You just designate the one company, and <i>Intelligent Reminder</i>
    informs you when you're at any of the branches of the company.</li>
    <li>Historical record is kept of need/location fulfillment.</li>
    <li>Voice Activation</li>
    </ul>
    
</asp:Content>
